name: Project Hundreds - Nonsense Game Jam #2
description:
WASD - Move

Space - Jump/Doublejump

Click - Eat

Made for the second Nonsense Game Jam - "There are hundreds"

This ended up being a lot simpler than my original plan, and there isn't really a goal to anything here. It's just a functional base engine prototype for a collectathon hoard kind of game.

I probably spent about 8hrs working on this total.
